comments.body:
@entdark that only really saves the matrix and clipping.

@Packiaseelan I don't think this is something that is supported in the way you may want, but you can do this by drawinf to a secondary canvas (such as one from a `SKPictureRecorder`). This will allow you to choose whether or not to draw the image to the main screen.

I don't believe there is a way undo/redo commands, but you can ask on the google forums: https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/skia-discuss
